article.headline: Army 76, Navy 71
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- Cleveland Richard scored 17 points and Josh Miller added 14 as Army edged Navy 76-71 on Sunday. The Black Knights (5-13, 1-3) led 33-26 at the half and shot 26-of-40 for the game. Adam Teague scored 16 points, and off the bench Clif Colbert scored 14 and Jordan Sugars added 13 for the Midshipmen (14-6, 3-2). Navy shot only 19-of-61 from the field.
